    chargebacks and therefore maximize the revenue. It can be used to detect

      description: Feedback the status of an order transaction.
      parameters:

          schema:
            type: string

          name: key

          name: format

            enum:
              - json
              - xml
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: action
          required: true
          schema:
            enum:
              - APPROVE
              - REJECT
              - REJECT_BLACKLIST
            type: string
        - allowEmptyValue: true

          name: notes
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
